text.section:
The regulations shall include:
Personnel training standards, including requirements for reasonable training, experience, and competency in:
Simple procedures used in drawing blood for cholesterol testing; and
The operation of blood chemical analyzers used for cholesterol screening;
Quality assurance standards;
Standards for counseling and referral procedures;
Standards for releasing and reporting test results; and
A prohibition on the payment of any sum to any person for bringing or referring a patient.
